---
// Componente de Servicios de Consultoría Senior
---

<section id="consultoria" class="py-24 px-6 relative bg-white/1">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    {/* Encabezado de Sección */}
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6"
    >
      <div class="max-w-xl text-left">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">
          Consultoría <span class="text-blue-500">Senior</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mb-4"></div>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          No solo escribo código; diseño el camino técnico para que tu negocio
          crezca sobre bases sólidas y resilientes.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:block h-px grow mx-12 bg-white/10 mb-6"></div>
    </div>

    {/* Rejilla de Servicios */}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pb-4">
      {/* Tarjeta 1: Modernización */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[40px] relative overflow-hidden group border-white/5 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-500/5 group-hover:bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full transition-all duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-blue-400 text-4xl"
            >settings_ethernet</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white text-left">
          Modernización Legacy
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-left text-sm">
          Rescate y evolución de lógica de negocio desde sistemas críticos en
          VB6 y .NET Legacy hacia arquitecturas modernas y escalables.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span>
            Refactorización Crítica
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span>
            Migración de Datos
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Tarjeta 2: Arquitectura Social */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[40px] relative overflow-hidden group border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-24 h-24 bg-emerald-500/5 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-full transition-all duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-emerald-400 text-4xl"
            >health_and_safety</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white text-left">
          Impacto Social
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-left text-sm">
          Sistemas de alta disponibilidad y respuesta rápida, como el núcleo de <strong
            >QRV+</strong
          >, enfocados en la seguridad y eficiencia.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
            UX de Emergencia
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
            Optimización de Carga
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Tarjeta 3: Estrategia de Producto */}
      <div
        class="glass-card p-10 rounded-[40px] relative overflow-hidden group border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-24 h-24 bg-purple-500/5 group-hover:bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full transition-all duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-purple-400 text-4xl"
            >architecture</span
          >
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white text-left">
          Visión de Negocio
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-left text-sm">
          Consultoría técnica para CEOs. Fusión de administración de empresas y
          código para optimizar presupuestos y tiempos de entrega.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></span>
            Dirección Técnica
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></span>
            Auditoría de Código
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      href="/proyectos"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-emerald-400 font-bold hover:gap-5 transition-all group"
    >
      Más Información <span
        class="material-symbols-rounded transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
        >arrow_forward</span
      >
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Efecto de sutil resplandor en el hover de las tarjetas */
  .glass-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }
</style>
